description: This file defines a React functional component named NewSwap, which renders a page allowing users to propose a new swap by filling out and submitting a form. It incorporates hooks for navigation and state management, and interacts with an API hook to handle swap creation.

methods.name: NewSwap()
methods.description: React functional component for proposing a new swap with a form.

methods.name: onSubmit
methods.description: Asynchronous handler invoked when the swap form is submitted; it creates a new swap via API and navigates back to the swaps list.
